110
00:05:10,050 --> 00:05:11,010
Alright, it's fine.

111
00:05:11,010 --> 00:05:12,930
You two, chairs, chairs.

112
00:05:12,930 --> 00:05:14,390
Sorry, sorry, sorry.

113
00:05:27,760 --> 00:05:28,930
Zhang, I've told you.

114
00:05:28,930 --> 00:05:29,770
Over there.

115
00:05:30,130 --> 00:05:31,020
Uncle Wang, there.

116
00:05:31,130 --> 00:05:32,010
Move that.

117
00:05:32,010 --> 00:05:33,780
