123
00:05:43,010 --> 00:05:43,960
Have a bottle of water.

124
00:05:43,960 --> 00:05:45,220
No, no, no need.

125
00:05:45,370 --> 00:05:47,370
Let's just record the violations.

126
00:05:47,370 --> 00:05:48,580
There's nowhere to sit.

127
00:05:49,730 --> 00:05:50,870
