Ms. Tang.

141
00:06:22,570 --> 00:06:23,950
What are you doing here?

142
00:06:24,760 --> 00:06:27,150
I came here with...

143
00:06:31,690 --> 00:06:34,580
Good for you.

144
00:06:35,130 --> 00:06:36,730
I came here to grab a bite.

145
00:06:36,730 --> 00:06:38,080
- Grab a bite?
- Yes, yes.

146
00:06:38,080 --> 00:06:39,240
The food here is quite good.

147
00:06:39,240 --> 00:06:40,220
Xu.

148
00:06:40,890 --> 00:06:41,730
Mr. Zhang.

149
00:06:41,930 --> 00:06:43,400
This is my leader, Ms. Tang.

150
00:06:43,400 --> 00:06:44,250
This is Mr. Zhang.

151
00:06:44,250 --> 00:06:45,660
No, no. Hello, hello.

152
00:06:45,840 --> 00:06:47,100
We're colleagues.

153
00:06:47,370 --> 00:06:48,210
Leader.

154
00:06:48,370 --> 00:06:49,220
Sorry, leader.

155
00:06:49,440 --> 00:06:51,370
This is occupying the road here.

156
00:06:51,370 --> 00:06:52,610
